              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/94602-kelly?shelf=owned">owned</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer53025675" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13074418101239508245">A lovely pyschological gem that seems to perfectly depict what it was like to be smart, rich and seventeen years old in 1954. I particularly liked the delicate, exquisite, admirably honest rendering of Cecile&apos;s emotions, whether ugly or sweet. I was that age not so very long ago- it isn&apos;t hard to remember the truth in what she&apos;s saying here.<br/><br/>Should be read in one sitting- with tea on an unhurried Sunday afternoon.</span>
  <span id="freeText13074418101239508245" style="display:none">A lovely pyschological gem that seems to perfectly depict what it was like to be smart, rich and seventeen years old in 1954. I particularly liked the delicate, exquisite, admirably honest rendering of Cecile's emotions, whether ugly or sweet. I was that age not so very long ago- it isn't hard to remember the truth in what she's saying here.<br /><br />Should be read in one sitting- with tea on an unhurried Sunday afternoon.</span>
  <a data-text-id="13074418101239508245" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


