<span id="freeTextContainer9492385236133792362">I’m not sure how I came to have this book on my wish list but I’m glad it was. Amazing to me that the author wrote this as a teen. It definitely comes across as a story written by someone young but I was very entertained. Apparently the book is a bit autobiographical. <br/><br/>Cecile loves her current life with her dad and is none to happy when he decides to settle down. The devious plan she concocts to keep her life as is has tragic consequences. <br/> <br/>If anyone reads the version I did, please don’t read the</span>
